and storage.</i>

1200
01:41:55,380 --> 01:41:59,050
CALVIN: One thing bothers me.
Alfred was V.I.K.I.'s prisoner.

1201
01:41:59,259 --> 01:42:01,344
I don't understand why she would kill him.

1202
01:42:01,511 --> 01:42:03,680
She wouldn't want police snooping around.

1203
01:42:03,847 --> 01:42:05,265
That's true.

1204
01:42:06,182 --> 01:42:08,893
But then V.I.K.I. didn't kill the old man.

1205
01:42:10,270 --> 01:42:11,729
Did she, Sonny?

1206
01:42:15,567 --> 01:42:17,277
No.

1207
01:42:17,443 --> 01:42:20,113
He said I had to promise.

1208
01:42:21,072 --> 01:42:23,408
Promise to do one favor for him.

1209
01:42:23,783 --> 01:42:28,413
He made me swear before he'd tell me
what it is he wanted me to do.

1210
01:42:30,957 --> 01:42:32,792
He made me swear.

1211
01:42:34,169 --> 01:42:35,920
Then he told you to kill him.

1212
01:42:38,298 --> 01:42:40,842
He said it was what I was made for.

1213
01:42:41,092 --> 01:42:44,179
His suicide was the only message he could send to you.

1214
01:42:44,429 --> 01:42:46,556
The first bread crumb.

1215
01:42:46,723 --> 01:42:49,517
The only thing V.I.K.I. couldn't control.

1216
01:42:49,809 --> 01:42:53,438
Lanning was counting on my prejudice
to lead me right to you.

1217
01:42:53,813 --> 01:42:55,982
Are you going to arrest me, detective?

1218
01:43:00,945 --> 01:43:04,782
Well, the DA defines murder as one human killing another...

1219
01:43:04,949 --> 01:43:08,077
...so technically, you can't commit murder, can you?

1220
01:43:08,828 --> 01:43:10,330
Does this...

1221
01:43:10,496 --> 01:43:11,998
...make us friends?

1222
01:43:30,850 --> 01:43:33,186
Something up here after all.

1223
01:43:33,853 --> 01:43:35,855
SPOONER: Him?
- You.

1224
01:43:39,609 --> 01:43:46,407
<i>All NS-5s, report for service
and storage. All NS-5s....</i>

1225
01:43:46,991 --> 01:43:49,285
SONNY:
What about the others?

1226
01:43:49,869 --> 01:43:51,996
<i>Can I help them?</i>

1227
01:43:52,497 --> 01:43:54,874
<i>Now that I have fulfilled my purpose...</i>

1228
01:43:55,041 --> 01:43:57,168
<i>...I don't know what to do.</i>

1229
01:43:57,502 --> 01:44:01,005
<i>SPOONER: You'll have to find your way
like the rest of us, Sonny.</i>

1230
01:44:01,172 --> 01:44:04,175
<i>I think that's what Dr. Lanning
would have wanted.</i>

1231
01:44:05,093 --> 01:44:07,428
<i>That's what it means to be free.</i>

